XP Pools:
- Act I Leoric Manor: 3 or 4 spawn locations
- Act I Southern Highlands - 1 spawn location south of the waypoint
- Act I Cemetery of the Forsaken - 3 spawn locations outside, 1 spawn location just inside each crypt
- Act I: Weeping Hollow + Fields of Misery
- Act II Howling Plateau - 3 spawn locations before you enter the city
- Act III Battlefields - go back up the stairs, 2 spawn locations
- Act III Bridge of Korski - 2 spawn locations
- Act III: Tower of the Cursed Level 1 + Tower of the Damned Level 1
